title: Peter Kay Live At The Albert Halls
description:
Peter Kay&#039;s &#039;Mum Wants A Bungalow Tour&#039; was a phenomenal success, sweeping across the country and seen by over 300,000 people. The 180 night record-breaking run in areas and theatres lasted an epic 9 months and still left people desperate for more.
Filmed in front of Peter&#039;s hometown crowd (Including his mum and his nan) Live At The Bolton Albert Halls is guaranteed to be the funniest stand-up you&#039;ll ever see.
